game.name: Zombie Shooter Deluxe
game.description:
There is no need to use the guns always to finish the waves of deadly zombies especially when you clear them from the area with just a few clicks on the screen. Yes, this time we have got you covered with a brand new action-packed challenge where you can make huge score without showing your aggressive moves. All you need to do is just click on the pictures of different zombies shown on the screen time to time in Zombie Shooter Deluxe.
You need to react fast to kill these blood-thirsty souls to clear each round. Use your magical hand to catch them and show the world that you have no mercy for these deadly souls! Be careful and try to kill the particular number of zombies before the time runs out in each round in this HTML5 shooting game! Remember you will have only a few lives to use which you can track by looking at the top left corner of the screen. 
The top left corner of the screen will show how many zombies you are left to be killed. Check out the top portion of the screen to track your score in the present round! Choose any mode out of three options including easy, medium and hard and get ready to enter the biggest zombie fun challenge for free! Play other free zombie simulator games on atmegame.com and get the best time online, no download required! Good luck to play more to get more!
